  "A type of cultural celebration, even when conditions shift significantly": "",
  "A taboo is a social or cultural prohibition against a particular behavior, practice, or topic. Taboos vary widely between cultures; what is taboo in one society may be perfectly acceptable in another.": "",
  "What does 'cultural imperialism' mean?": "",
  "The dominance of one culture over others, often through media, economic power, or political influence, imposing cultural values and practices": "",
